{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/creer-un-bot-sur-discord","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"5a887609-4aa3-597f-a1de-4b90cb75a7c8","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f9ed5bfdf757d85746e804bacc51d191/29d31/7-discord-bots-to-enhance-your-server.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.08333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f9ed5bfdf757d85746e804bacc51d191/8ac56/7-discord-bots-to-enhance-your-server.webp 240w,\n/static/f9ed5bfdf757d85746e804bacc51d191/d3be9/7-discord-bots-to-enhance-your-server.webp 480w,\n/static/f9ed5bfdf757d85746e804bacc51d191/426ac/7-discord-bots-to-enhance-your-server.webp 700w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f9ed5bfdf757d85746e804bacc51d191/09b79/7-discord-bots-to-enhance-your-server.jpg 240w,\n/static/f9ed5bfdf757d85746e804bacc51d191/7cc5e/7-discord-bots-to-enhance-your-server.jpg 480w,\n/static/f9ed5bfdf757d85746e804bacc51d191/29d31/7-discord-bots-to-enhance-your-server.jpg 700w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/f9ed5bfdf757d85746e804bacc51d191/29d31/7-discord-bots-to-enhance-your-server.jpg\"\n          alt=\"7 discord bots to enhance your server\"\n          title=\"7 discord bots to enhance your server\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Vous l’aurez donc compris, il fonctionnera en JavaScript mais il existe d’autres librairies, notamment en Python, Java, PHP, C#, etc. Voici une liste des librairies disponibles : <a href=\"https://discordapi.com/unofficial/libs.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://discordapi.com/unofficial/libs.html</a></p>\n<p>Le prérequis pour ce tutoriel est d’avoir un serveur NodeJS (minimum v.6.0.0) installé, ainsi qu’un compte discord.</p>\n<h1 id=\"création-de-lapplication\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cr%C3%A9ation-de-lapplication\" aria-label=\"création de lapplication permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Création de l’application</h1>\n<p>Afin d’avoir un bot disponible sur son serveur, il faut se rendre sur <a href=\"https://discordapp.com/developers/docs/intro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">la partie developper</a> du site de Discord afin de créer une nouvelle application.\nPour ce faire, allez dans <strong>“My Apps”</strong> et cliquez sur <strong>“New app”</strong>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/1ffbd/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/8ac56/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.webp 240w,\n/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/d3be9/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.webp 480w,\n/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/e46b2/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.webp 960w,\n/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/f992d/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.webp 1440w,\n/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/882b9/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.webp 1920w,\n/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/d21eb/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.webp 2108w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/8ff5a/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.png 240w,\n/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/e85cb/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.png 480w,\n/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/d9199/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.png 960w,\n/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/07a9c/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.png 1440w,\n/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/29114/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.png 1920w,\n/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/1ffbd/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.png 2108w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/23a8ac6debc491429a3b47959bcc27fd/d9199/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12.png\"\n          alt=\"Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12\"\n          title=\"Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-16.58.12\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Remplissez le formulaire (voir screen) et cliquez sur <strong>“Create App”</strong>.\nIl suffit ensuite de convertir votre App en Bot en cliquant sur le bouton <strong>“Create a Bot User”</strong> :\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/6b95e/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.166666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/8ac56/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.webp 240w,\n/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/d3be9/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.webp 480w,\n/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/e46b2/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.webp 960w,\n/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/f992d/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.webp 1440w,\n/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/bb4a2/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.webp 1458w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/8ff5a/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.png 240w,\n/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/e85cb/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.png 480w,\n/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/d9199/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.png 960w,\n/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/07a9c/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.png 1440w,\n/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/6b95e/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.png 1458w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/06fa782eb60d1caa0628041a1282cd8b/d9199/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46.png\"\n          alt=\"Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46\"\n          title=\"Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.02.46\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Vous obtiendrez alors un écran spécifique avec le token de votre Bot. Notez le bien, on en aura besoin plus tard.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/a5120/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/8ac56/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.webp 240w,\n/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/d3be9/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.webp 480w,\n/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/e46b2/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.webp 960w,\n/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/f992d/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.webp 1440w,\n/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/882b9/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.webp 1920w,\n/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/4391b/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.webp 2380w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/8ff5a/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.png 240w,\n/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/e85cb/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.png 480w,\n/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/d9199/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.png 960w,\n/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/07a9c/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.png 1440w,\n/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/29114/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.png 1920w,\n/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/a5120/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.png 2380w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/2636a225a92532209256dd3f9015e933/d9199/Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04.png\"\n          alt=\"Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04\"\n          title=\"Screen-Shot-2017-12-03-at-17.01.04\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"initialisation-et-configuration\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#initialisation-et-configuration\" aria-label=\"initialisation et configuration permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Initialisation et configuration</h1>\n<p>Démarrez un nouveau projet et installez <code class=\"language-text\">Discord.js</code> à l’aide de NPM :<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ npm install --save discord.js</code></p>\n<p>Créez ensuite un fichier <code class=\"language-text\">bot.js</code> et mettez ceci dedans :</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Discord <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"discord.js\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> client <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Discord<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Client</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nclient<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'ready'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Logged in as </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>client<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>user<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tag<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">!</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nclient<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">msg</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>msg<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>content <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'ping'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    msg<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">reply</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Pong!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nclient<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">login</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'token'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Remplacez <code class=\"language-text\">token</code> par celui de votre application, et exécutez la commande :<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ node bot.js</code></p>\n<p>Votre bot est désormais connecté sur votre serveur. Pour le moment, il ne répond qu’au message <strong>ping</strong> mais libre à vous d’ajouter des commandes.</p>\n<p>Vous pouvez diffuser de la musique ou des sons, récupérer des infos depuis des API, faire du scrapping ou vous notifier de différentes choses, les possibilités sont multiples.</p>\n<p>Voici la <a href=\"https://discord.js.org/#/docs/main/stable/general/welcome\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">documentation complète de Discord.js</a> afin de vous donner des idées. Ou bien encore mon bot, disponible sur <a href=\"https://github.com/Enishowk/Bot-Discord\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">mon GitHub</a>.</p>\n<p>Je présenterai des fonctionnalités plus poussée dans une autre partie. Si vous avez des questions ou des suggestions, je suis disponible sur <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Enish__\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a>.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/creer-un-bot-sur-discord","tagSlugs":["/tag/blog/","/tag/dev/","/tag/bot/","/tag/discord/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2017-12-03","description":"Créer un bot sur Discord est quelques chose de très simple. Bien qu'il existe plusieurs façon de faire, je vous propose de le faire fonctionner à l'aide de NodeJS et du module discord.js.","tags":["Blog","Dev","Bot","Discord"],"title":"Créer un bot sur Discord"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/creer-un-bot-sur-discord"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1307906156","251939775","401334301"]}